Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:02.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we come!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.33,0:00:04.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time for Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:06.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're going to gather all the shards\nof the Sacred Jewel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:08.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'll destroy Naraku\nwith my Tetsusaiga!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:11.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The saintly mummy of Hakushin\nwho saved so many people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}has disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:14.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the barrier broken\non the sacred island of Hijiri,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:18.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha and Bankotsu are back at full\nstrength and locked in their final battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:20.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's up to us and Miroku,\NSango, Shippo and Kirara!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:22.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Travel back in time\nfor a Feudal Fairy Tale!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:24.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give me power, Father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:20.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is what created\nthe barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.44,0:02:23.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But this ornament was\nlocked up in the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:29.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Saint Hakushin lending\nhis powers to Naraku?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:44.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That disgusting barrier\nis finally gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's do it once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank goodness his\ndemonic powers are restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:59.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Inuyasha is at a disadvantage.\NHe's hurt his left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha, will you be all right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:06.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bankotsu has two Sacred Jewel\nshards in his halberd Banryu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:11.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's see you do it right this {\i1}time....{\i0}\NLet me see this Wind Scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't need advice from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:16.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.06,0:03:18.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:24.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dragon Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:29.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bankotsu {\i1}stopped....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:31.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:35.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just need to look\nfor the miasmic whirlpool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been waiting to use\nmy Backlash Wave!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:41.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?! I don't see a demonic aura\naround Bankotsu!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:44.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I can't use the Backlash Wave?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't stand there in a daze!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:50.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:55.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ahh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel like a weight's been\nlifted off my {\i1}shoulders....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're conscious, Shippo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:04.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All I remember is that\NI started feeling sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:09.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You fainted from the sacred\nbarrier of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:12.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems to have purified\nyour demonic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:15.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.62,0:04:18.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's having a tough time\nfighting off Bankotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:28.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess you were gonna\ntry something,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, keep it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha's arm has been injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:39.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is it bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, Kirara!\NHelp Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He won't last long\nwith that arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:05:00.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bankotsu is a specter,\nbut he was once human.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:06.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the scope of his strength means\nhe's using some kind of demon power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:10.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Backlash Wave is a technique\nthat surrounds and reverses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,the flow of an opponent's\ndemonic aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:17.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But since Bankotsu was once human,\nhe doesn't produce any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:22.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Shikon Jewel shards want me\nto destroy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:28.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The black light of a tainted shard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:36.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bankotsu is using the powers\nof the Shikon Jewel shards in his halberd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:41.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I know,\NI can use my Backlash Wave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:47.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's thought of something.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:50.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't fall for the same trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you think I would keep\nusing the same attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:05:58.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:00.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He summoned a thunder storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, what's he scheming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:21.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:22.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:23.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dragon Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:29.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't predict where they'll fall, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tons of lightning bolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:36.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He won't be able to\nuse the Backlash Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:45.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out, Shintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:48.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, don't leave the {\i1}barrier....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:52.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:53.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Aghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:34.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:36.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:39.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kago....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:01.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You dare....hurt....Kagome....!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:11.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't predict where\nmy Dragon Thunder will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you just lie there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.73,0:08:19.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll cut you and your sword into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:25.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:39.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, {\i1}you....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This match {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:46.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,just between you and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.76,0:08:51.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You didn't have to involve\NKagome and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:57.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit being so naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quit using the same techinque!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:16.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How many dirty tricks must\nyou pull before you're satisfied?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:17.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's no dirty or fair\nin a match to the death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:30.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll take you down even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Arghh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:00.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:39.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Saint Hakushin's altar {\i1}ornament....{\i0}\NAs I {\i1}expected....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.98,0:10:47.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saint Hakushin's...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:51.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The demonic aura around the\NTetsusaiga has been purified...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:52.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}vajra....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:58.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,was at the core of the sacred barrier\naround this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:00.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems Saint {\i1}Hakushin....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is an ally of Bankotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:10.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess he wants me to\nfinish you off quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:14.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although it bothers me that he\ndoesn't have faith in my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:19.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Too bad this has to end, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:39.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Woman....{\i0} Why {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:41.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:46.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His arm turned to bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:56.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A sacred arrow? So she's\NKikyo's reincarnation?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:10.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:15.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bankotsu {\i1}is....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.37,0:12:16.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why {\i1}you....{\i0} Bankotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bankotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:44.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:50.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! A barrier!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.58,0:13:03.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's gone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:05.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:11.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....but....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:15.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only Bankotsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:20.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the vajra is also gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It helped Bankotsu escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:25.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:31.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Saint {\i1}Hakushin....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:37.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where has Saint Hakushin gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, I feel awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell happened, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:11.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bankotsu....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kohaku and Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:18.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is this?\NIt feels awful here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:24.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not a very nice place for\nmen of evil thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:28.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But you're okay?\NNo wonder you're a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.03,0:14:31.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not a ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:44.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. The light from the\nvajra enveloped me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:53.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is {\i1}that....?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the Saint Hakushin\NInuyasha kept talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:08.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is Saint Hakushin's mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the mummy who created the\nbarriers around Mt. Hakurei and Hijiri Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:24.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:27.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,died protecting the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.66,0:15:33.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Saint Hakushin disappeared from\nthe island because of
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:36.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,a demon known as Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:39.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Father died fighting Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:43.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see. He died honorably.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:46.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our father's bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.58,0:15:48.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We will give him a proper funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:15:59.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:01.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Koga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:09.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Great! We finally caught up\nto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.67,0:16:15.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I chased it until it\nran in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Meat! Meat! Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:18.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.95,0:16:26.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kinda reminds me of home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.45,0:16:30.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it feels bad in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.29,0:16:31.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because of the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:35.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A barrier protects the mountain
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so demons like us\ncan't get near it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:39.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and permeates even this cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Man, that's cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:42.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We leave after we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:43.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:49.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Band of Seven are hiding\ninside the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll find a way to get through this\nbarrier no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:56.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shintaro! Sisters!\NTake care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:00.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll pray for your good journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If for some reason,\nyou ever feel lonely,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:09.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,please don't hesitate to call on {\i1}me....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's enough, Monk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:26.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wow!\NLook at this valley, Jaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even though we're far away\nfrom Mt. Hakurei,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I still feel awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:38.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The purifying aura that keeps out\nanything demonic reaches all the way here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you up to, Naraku?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:54.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lord Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:54.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.21,0:17:59.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Rin, don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:06.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't go too fast.\NI'll fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:13.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please don't scream like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- How annoying!\N- I can't take {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady Kikyo, must you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.03,0:18:26.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forgive me.\NI wanted to stay longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:29.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,First, Dr. {\i1}Suikotsu....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:32.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,now, even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:38.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I hoped you would stay\nuntil Dr. Suikotsu returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:43.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,After all that happened,\nyou still wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.79,0:18:49.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dr. Suikotsu suffered in pain sometimes,\nbut he was kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:55.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The virtuous side of Suikotsu\nprotected these children.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:57.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:01.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you meet Dr. Suikotsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,please tell him that we\nare waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:07.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuta....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:13.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.66,0:19:27.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because of Mt. Hakurei's barrier,\nhe disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:34.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuta, Chiyo... the Suikotsu\nyou knew is no longer...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:44.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The barrier has become\nstronger since.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:47.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've reached my limit, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The power of the barrier\nis becoming stronger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:09.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The barrier is making Shippo\nso {\i1}dizzy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:14.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey Miroku, you sure Naraku is\nhiding in Mt. Hakurei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.91,0:20:20.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure that Saint Hakushin is\nthe one creating this barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:25.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And the Saint protected\NBankotsu, one of Naraku's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'd have thought that a mass of\nevil air like Naraku
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,wouldn't be able\nto enter a sacred place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:37.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But once inside,\nthere's no better place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:39.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are those after {\i1}him....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:44.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Wolf-Demon Koga,\NSesshomaru and you, Inuyasha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:48.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As well as Lady {\i1}Kikyo....{\i0} All are unable\nto go to Mt. Hakurei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, {\i1}you....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:58.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango and I will check\nout Mt. Hakurei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:20:59.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha and Kagome,\nyou wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But just the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:06.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch over Kirara.\NI can't take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sango....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:10.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:16.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,From this point on, even I won't be\nable fondle Sango's {\i1}body....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.91,0:21:18.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're doing it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.34,0:21:21.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not worried about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:25.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't even know what's\ninside the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:31.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Inuyasha can't go in.\NIt has to be the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:32.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:39.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sango, {\i1}Miroku....{\i0} Just check around.\NDon't take any risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Exactly our intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:44.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:55.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will they be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:22:00.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We just have to\nhave faith in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:47.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Band of Seven?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.96,0:23:48.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They've taken refuge\ninside Mt. Hakurei!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:55.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn it! Ginkotsu! Renkotsu!\NCome on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:59.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is bad! Koga is trapped\nin the steel threads!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:03.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If he gets dragged inside,\nhe'll be purified!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.01,0:24:08.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Koga's Solitary Battle!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.81,0:24:11.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where are their Shikon Jewel shards?!
